their own culture.

615
00:49:50,787 --> 00:49:54,621
It took hundreds of years,
and it evolved over time.

616
00:49:54,691 --> 00:49:57,922
That's gone in America.

617
00:49:57,995 --> 00:50:02,364
People now don't even have
any concept that there ever was...

618
00:50:02,432 --> 00:50:05,731
