that's created to make money.

619
00:50:05,802 --> 00:50:09,329
Whatever's the biggest, latest thing,
they're into it.

620
00:50:09,406 --> 00:50:12,898
You just get disgusted after a while
with humanity...

621
00:50:12,976 --> 00:50:15,342
for not having more,
kind of like...

622
00:50:15,412 --> 00:50:21,214
